-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>Asans\u00f6rlerinizin hem emniyet hem de uzun s\u00fcre kullan\u0131m\u0131 a\u00e7\u0131s\u0131ndan periyodik bak\u0131m anla\u015fmas\u0131yla s\u00fcrekli hizmet veriyoruz.<\/p>\n<p>Asans\u00f6rler kullan\u0131m esnas\u0131nda \u00e7e\u015fitli etkenlere maruz kalmaktad\u0131rlar. Kullan\u0131m hatalar\u0131, malzeme a\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131 gibi ola\u011fan sebeplerden ar\u0131za yapabilece\u011fi gibi yetersiz bak\u0131mdan kaynaklanabilen ar\u0131zalar nedeniyle de hizmet veremez duruma gelir ve buna ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak b\u00fcy\u00fck \u00e7apta tadilatlar b\u00fcy\u00fck masraflar gerektirebilir.<\/p>\n<p>Mevcut asans\u00f6r y\u00f6netmeli\u011finde de belirtildi\u011fi gibi asans\u00f6rlerde s\u00fcrekli periyodik bak\u0131m yap\u0131lmas\u0131 zorunludur. Bak\u0131m hizmetini y\u00fcklenen firman\u0131n \u201cTSE hizmet yeterlilik belgesi ve sanayi ticaret bakanl\u0131\u011f\u0131 sat\u0131\u015f sonras\u0131 hizmet yeterlilik\u201d belgesi almas\u0131 gerekmektedir. Tekin As Asans\u00f6r bak\u0131m hizmetini, tesisin \u00f6zelliklerine g\u00f6re belirlenen periyotlarda uzman kadrosuyla y\u00fcr\u00fctmektedir.<\/p>\n<p>Asans\u00f6rleriniz kullan\u0131m hatalar\u0131, malzeme a\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131 veya yetersiz bak\u0131mdan kaynaklanan sebeplerden dolay\u0131 ar\u0131za yapabilir. Bu gibi istenmeyen durumlarda firmam\u0131z periyodik bak\u0131m anla\u015fmas\u0131 olan veya olmayan t\u00fcm binalara g\u00fcn\u00fcn her saati Acil M\u00fcdahale hizmeti vermektedir.<\/p>\n<p>Asans\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fczde s\u0131k s\u0131k ar\u0131zalar meydana geliyor ve s\u00fcrekli artan maliyetlerden \u015fikayet ediyorsan\u0131z, Tekin As Asans\u00f6re gelin s\u00fcrekli bak\u0131m anla\u015fmas\u0131 yapal\u0131m bu sorunlardan sizi tamamen kurtaral\u0131m.<\/p>\n<p>Asans\u00f6r bak\u0131m\u0131 ne yaz\u0131k ki \u00fclkemizde \u00e7ok dikkate al\u0131nmamas\u0131 nedeniyle \u00f6l\u00fcml\u00fc yada yaralanmal\u0131 \u00e7ok s\u0131k kazalar\u0131n\u0131n ya\u015fanmas\u0131na sebep olmaktad\u0131r. Tekin As Asans\u00f6r, tespit edilen ar\u0131zalar\u0131 h\u0131zl\u0131 bir \u015fekilde \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r hale getirmek i\u00e7in g\u00fcvenilir bir hizmet sunmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Bak\u0131m &#038; Onar\u0131m Hizmetleri Asans\u00f6rlerinizin hem emniyet hem de uzun s\u00fcre kullan\u0131m\u0131 a\u00e7\u0131s\u0131ndan periyodik bak\u0131m anla\u015fmas\u0131yla s\u00fcrekli hizmet veriyoruz. Asans\u00f6rler kullan\u0131m esnas\u0131nda \u00e7e\u015fitli etkenlere maruz kalmaktad\u0131rlar. Kullan\u0131m hatalar\u0131, malzeme a\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131 gibi ola\u011fan sebeplerden ar\u0131za yapabilece\u011fi gibi yetersiz bak\u0131mdan kaynaklanabilen ar\u0131zalar nedeniyle de hizmet veremez duruma gelir ve buna ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak b\u00fcy\u00fck \u00e7apta tadilatlar b\u00fcy\u00fck masraflar [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":725,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-739","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.tekinasasansor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/739","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.tekinasasansor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.tekinasasansor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.tekinasasansor.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.tekinasasan